Name: OverTheSpeedLimit
About the game: Over The Speed Limit A challenging racing game where speed is everything . Put your racing skills to the test and race in different conditions where loosing friction can cost you the 1st place . Play with the in car camera for a vr perspective (vr compatible) . Win Races , make money , unlock access to new racing levels , new racing classes , Drag races , and customization . Racing classes : normal cars class Customised cars class Sports car class Higher classes need more attention to braking and slowing down in corners . Adding more cars is subject to consider in the future . The use of a Steering wheel is supported and recommended for this game. Note : For full gamepad support , the gamepad needs to be properly installed on Windows with an installed driver , otherwise you will only have partlial gamepad functionality (the gamepad will work only on game play ).
